whois slash16.org | grep "Name Server" | tr '[:lower:]' '[:upper:]' | sort | uniq -u

whois command details all the ifno about a domain name, from ip's to registrar, to server address, to owner address etc.

NAME SERVER: NS-1236.AWSDNS-26.ORG
NAME SERVER: NS-144.AWSDNS-18.COM
NAME SERVER: NS-1989.AWSDNS-56.CO.UK
NAME SERVER: NS-686.AWSDNS-21.NET
